🔑 KEY CHANGES - SlippageCheck Integration

BREAKING CHANGE: Parameter names updated for adding liquidity

  When ADDING liquidity (mint/increase):
    ❌ OLD: amount0Min, amount1Min
    ✅ NEW: amount0Max, amount1Max
    
  When REMOVING liquidity (decrease):
    ✅ Unchanged: amount0Min, amount1Min

Affected Functions:
  • swapAndMint() - Now uses amount0Max/amount1Max
  • swapAndIncreaseLiquidity() - Now uses amount0Max/amount1Max
  • moveRange() - Now uses amount0Max/amount1Max
  • decreaseAndSwap() - Still uses amount0Min/amount1Min ✅

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

🚀 QUICK START

Start all services:

  # Terminal 1
  cd packages/ponder && pnpm dev
  
  # Terminal 2
  cd packages/backend && npm run dev
  
  # Terminal 3
  cd packages/frontend && npm run dev

Access points:
  Frontend:  http://localhost:3000
  Backend:   http://localhost:3001
  Ponder:    http://localhost:42069

